{"tid":1363244,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[727 元朗重要資訊] 啲人成日問點對準政權 我終於諗到點答你","createTime":"2019-07-25T06:16:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T10:51:42.000Z","uid":5780,"like":19,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"558ba8c133200cc9a5a933d1e573a7b50061fd2b","tid":1363244,"uid":5780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T06:16:58.000Z","msg":"以下是政治學討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好多人問，如果727做法好似721白衫咁，見村都搞，咁<span style=\"color: red;\">同黑社會有乜野分別</span>？<br />\n人地又唔似政府咁，有立法會，有政總，點<span style=\"color: red;\">對準政權</span>呀？<br />\n我可以答你，係有！<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">十八鄉鄉事委員會!!!<br />\n佢就好似十八鄉嘅<span style=\"color: red;\">政府</span>咁<br />\n</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JhDWZRd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJhDWZRd.png&h=2b8e0d87&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nGoogle map: <a href=\"https://www.google.com/maps/place/Sap+Pat+Heung+Rural+Committee/@22.4438641,114.0345038,18.67z/data=!4m8!1m2!2m1!1z5Y2B5YWr6YSJ6YSJ5LqL5aeU5ZOh5pyD!3m4!1s0x3403f0a7af1f8e55:0x6dbb17740163524c!8m2!3d22.44419!4d114.034401?hl=en\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Fmaps%2Fplace%2FSap%2BPat%2BHeung%2BRural%2BCommittee%2F%4022.4438641%2C114.0345038%2C18.67z%2Fdata%3D%214m8%211m2%212m1%211z5Y2B5YWr6YSJ6YSJ5LqL5aeU5ZOh5pyD%213m4%211s0x3403f0a7af1f8e55%3A0x6dbb17740163524c%218m2%213d22.44419%214d114.034401%3Fhl%3Den&d=9aIS%2Fhk2hxf5w8hb7WAMUS9NcCfN%2BV0%2B2kMkFhSspzA%3D&h=86f067b5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com/maps/place/Sap+Pat+Heung+Rural+Committee/@22.4438641,114.0345038,18.67z/data=!4m8!1m2!2m1!1z5Y2B5YWr6YSJ6YSJ5LqL5aeU5ZOh5pyD!3m4!1s0x3403f0a7af1f8e55:0x6dbb17740163524c!8m2!3d22.44419!4d114.034401?hl=en</a><br />\n<br />\n一、當元朗遊行不反對通知書後，十八鄉鄉事委員會主席出言恐嚇：「一切嚴重後果將全部由警方負責」，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">高調阻嚇</span></strong>市民參與遊行，嚴重破壞社會安寧。<br />\n<br />\n二、十八鄉鄉事委員就好似成個十八鄉既<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>村公所</strong></span>咁，係村既政權集中地，「十八鄉鄉事委員會於1949年成立，初時稱為「十八鄉鄉公所」，是官民溝通橋樑的民意代表機構，協助政府施政及維持地方秩序，調解村民糾紛，促進鄉村福利，改善地方衛生及清潔，發展農業及林務和培植教育與文化。」"},{"pid":"2d0b52ec2c111c1d7adba5df50b07d493c44e515","tid":1363244,"uid":5780,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T06:18:20.000Z","msg":"三、交通方便，間野係馬路邊，又近西鐵站，附近又冇村，唔怕阻到良民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WnS8Q17.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWnS8Q17.png&h=a7284a53&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pxfN6At.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpxfN6At.png&h=e5f4213a&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TnHXKm8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTnHXKm8.png&h=8bdd01ad&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2odv4m9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2odv4m9.png&h=206df094&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f3704a68b88b7452d413e0388a4705768c9ec732","tid":1363244,"uid":5780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T06:19:07.000Z","msg":"歡迎大家繼續政治討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d541eb9de000f4159d635c5f116557bd8787b89","tid":1363244,"uid":5780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T06:19:37.000Z","msg":"覺竹有用嘅麻煩推一推，謝"},{"pid":"ed0bdc2b49a97d698517d66c7b22556204526c4b","tid":1363244,"uid":5780,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8d541eb9de000f4159d635c5f116557bd8787b89","tid":1363244,"uid":5780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T06:19:37.000Z","msg":"覺竹有用嘅麻煩推一推，謝"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T06:20:31.000Z","msg":"覺<span style=\"color: red;\">得</span>有用嘅麻煩推一推，謝"},{"pid":"4b117eff8590ad8abcb26740653443902a2e0b96","tid":1363244,"uid":212182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20